attributes.value: Within 24 hours of purchase, 75% of the funds will be sent and can be verified through wallet address 0xc19E2A5F48D9de8c33cA08817421FCac605A1E23. Proof of payment will be provided for account verification. Additionally, we will furnish a receipt for each transaction as proof of donation towards the support of breast cancer awareness, which will also be attached to the site and provided within 24 hours. Minus fees GWEI.
